ROOT does this with its own preprocessor and custom comment decorators.  like:<p><pre><code>    class mydata
   {

        /* simple type */
        int n; 

       /* the following array is of length n */
        double  * v; //[n]       

      /* don&#x27;t serialize the following */ 
      int reference_count; //! 

     ClassDef(mydata,1) ; // this macro does some magic, 1 is the version number etc.
   };</code></pre>
